          </div>
          <a href={base + "/contact"} class="btn-sm">Inquire Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="room-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540555700478-4be289fbecef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=75" alt="Premier Nipa Hut Garden View" class="room-img" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="room-body">
          <div class="room-type">Premier</div>
          <div class="room-name">Premier Nipa Hut — Garden View</div>
          <div class="room-features">Spacious premier room with private garden terrace. More room, more light, more quiet. Wake up to green rather than the break — the calm room.</div>
          <div class="room-amenities">
